nation with different communication styles\n- Technology failure scenarios requiring focus adaptation\n- Multiple simultaneous crisis management\n- Focus maintenance under extreme time pressure and fatigue	f	2025-09-26 04:33:44	2025-09-26 04:33:44	2025-10-24 09:20:27.319172	Updated via trigger
